titleStmt.title: News from Whetstones Parke, or, A relation of the late bloody battle there, between the bawds and whores, and how both parties after a sharp dispute, and much loss on either side, were at last reconciled by the mediation of the pimps and hectors, with the articles of peace concluded upon between them.
